headline: Team With $100 Million in Assets Joins Ameriprise Financial to Fulfill Growth Aspirations
summary: MINNEAPOLIS, March 25, 2025--Financial advisors Mila Kisz, MBA, and Roman Kisz, AAMS®, CRPS®, recently joined the independent channel of Ameriprise Financial, Inc. (NYSE:AMP) from Edward Jones where they managed $100 million in client assets. The married duo joined an established Ameriprise practice, LegacyOak Advisors, in Simi Valley, Calif., led by financial advisor Greg Lewandowski.
